animeTitle: Super Dragon Ball Heroes Meteor Mission
otherNames: スーパードラゴンボールヒーローズ, 魔の侵略者編, The Demon Invader Saga
synopsis:
The Demon Invader Saga (魔の侵略者編 Ma no Shinryakusha Hen, lit. "Demon Invader Arc") is the ninth original saga of Dragon Ball Heroes.

It continues on from where the Supreme Kai of Time Saga of Super Dragon Ball Heroes left off.
